          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Lifesaving Librarians Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration to establish a grant program for public libraries that are in designated high-intensity drug trafficking areas to purchase naloxone and train employees in naloxone administration.</p>]]></text>
